en_125261_0	All arrangements are made to celebrate Sri Lanka’s 68 th Independence Day, the Minister of Home Affairs Wajira Abeywardana said.
en_125261_1	Under the theme ‘Ekama Deyak, Maha Balayak’ (One Nation, Great Power) the event will take place in Galle Face Green on Thursday (04).
en_125261_2	A special bus service is also in place for the participants.
en_125261_3	Meanwhile, traffic through roundabout at Galle Face Green to Parliament will be limited from 5am to 12pm.
